Westlite brings happiness to our residents by providing a secure, warm and caring, comfortable and convenient living community, delivered with the best service quality to our customers and partners. We will provide a safe and secure living community with on-site security. We are looking for suitable Security Personnel for assets located at Gul, Tuas, Ayer Rajah Crescent or Kallang.

Responsibilities

  General Screening of People / Staff / Vehicle
  Guarding and Patrolling
  Access and Egress control
  Incident Response e.g Fire Alarm, Lift Breakdown etc
  Manage Security and Safety Systems (Fire, Lift, CCtV systems etc)
  Key Press Management

Requirements

  PWM-certified Security Officer
  Able to perform 12-hour rotating shifts (2 day shifts, 2 night shifts, 1 off day and 1 rest day)
  Good command of English
  Experience in foreign worker dormitory or handling large groups of foreign workers would be advantageous

Other Information

  Competitive Salary Package&nbsp;
  Contract of 1 year service, may be renewable thereafter
  Monthly $400 allowance
  Average 10 Off / Rest days per month
  AWS
  Variable Bonus
  Annual Leave
  Birthday Leave
  Dental Consulation, Health Screening or Vision Care Benefits of $400 a year
  Company Medical Insurance

